# HEARTBEAT.md

Lightweight checks when you want a **fresh snapshot** of the stack (e.g. after upgrades). Details and commands live in **`TOOLS.md`**.

- [ ] Dashboard `GET /api/health` — any service `"ok": false`?
- [ ] Model Gateway `GET /v1/models` — expected models listed?
- [ ] MCP — `servers.txt` / dashboard MCP tab matches what you expect?
- [ ] OpenClaw — Control UI on **6680** (not 6682); gateway token in `.env`?
- [ ] Update the **Last verified** block at the top of **`TOOLS.md`** when done.
